{
  "id": "64d1f5989bd3ef001c258763",
  "title": "「ナメられたら殺す」という侍みたいな価値観のあるコミュニティ",
  "created": 1691481501,
  "updated": 1773796151,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "64d1f5989bd3ef001c258763",
      "text": "「ナメられたら殺す」という侍みたいな価値観のあるコミュニティ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691481501,
      "updated": 1691481501
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f599ed60e60000405e8c",
      "text": "[メンツ]を大事にするとも言えそう",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691481501,
      "updated": 1691482422
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f5aced60e60000405e8e",
      "text": "\t[警察]はメンツを大事にするらしいので該当しそう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691481518,
      "updated": 1691485234
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f5d3ed60e60000405e90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691481557,
      "updated": 1691481557
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f5d5ed60e60000405e91",
      "text": "[ヤンキー]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691481558,
      "updated": 1691485226
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f5dfed60e60000405e92",
      "text": "[反社会的勢力]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691481569,
      "updated": 1691485229
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f6b979d3a90000b8ccb5",
      "text": "[政治家]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691481786,
      "updated": 1691485231
    },
    {
      "id": "64d214b8ed60e60000ee15f6",
      "text": "[薩摩]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691489466,
      "updated": 1691489474
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f5eaed60e60000405e93",
      "text": " [薩摩ホグワーツ]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691481579,
      "updated": 1691489475
    },
    {
      "id": "64d20e87e60035000078dbac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691487880,
      "updated": 1691487880
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f5f4ed60e60000405e94",
      "text": "あとそういう中小企業がありそう？[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691481589,
      "updated": 1691481610
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9e2690000000000170328",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1773789802,
      "updated": 1773789802
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f98c55cbd300006f5289",
      "text": "[/mtane0412/名誉の文化][mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1691482508,
      "updated": 1773796151
    },
    {
      "id": "64d1f98c55cbd300006f528a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1691482508,
      "updated": 1691482508
    },
    {
      "id": "64d212b25b98c20000db4e67",
      "text": "「愛されるより恐れられるほうがよい」という考え方 [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1691488947,
      "updated": 1691489274
    },
    {
      "id": "64d213f95b98c20000db4e6a",
      "text": " [君主論]だっけ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1691489274,
      "updated": 1691489274
    },
    {
      "id": "64d3037b1280f00000570195",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1691550588,
      "updated": 1691550588
    },
    {
      "id": "64d3037b1280f00000570196",
      "text": "会社組織ならありそう(いやほんとはだめだけど)[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1691550588,
      "updated": 1691550594
    },
    {
      "id": "64d3037c1280f00000570197",
      "text": "ネット上のコミュニティなんかでもあるのかな",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1691550589,
      "updated": 1691550591
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9e26e0000000000170329",
      "text": "\t会社は階層的な組織はこれだと思ってる[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1773789806,
      "updated": 1773789938
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9e276000000000017032a",
      "text": "\t\t皆に見える場で平社員の[sta.icon]とやりとりできる管理職以上は見たことがない",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1773789814,
      "updated": 1773789831
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9e286000000000017032b",
      "text": "\t\tテキストだと勝てない、舐められるからこういう手段そのものを封じてくる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1773789831,
      "updated": 1773789947
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9e2fe000000000017032e",
      "text": "\t\t\t怒られる + やりとりも消せ、とか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1773789951,
      "updated": 1773789958
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9f72f00000000006e5e48",
      "text": "\t\tあるいは「殺す」じゃなくて「殺されるかもしれない」という受動的な理由かもしれないが",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1773795120,
      "updated": 1773795135
    },
    {
      "id": "69b9e2ab000000000017032c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1773789867,
      "updated": 1773789947
    },
    {
      "id": "64d39b8ae5172d00004cf424",
      "text": "[決闘]？[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1691589515,
      "updated": 1691589526
    },
    {
      "id": "69b921430000000000cccd90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773740355,
      "updated": 1773740355
    },
    {
      "id": "69b921450000000000cccd91",
      "text": "殺された人専用のチャットルームで盛り上がりたい[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1773740357,
      "updated": 1773740375
    },
    {
      "id": "64dcfcd35b98c200003ceeea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1692204244,
      "updated": 1692204244
    },
    {
      "id": "64dcfcd45b98c200003ceeeb",
      "text": "[ナメられたら殺す]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1692204244,
      "updated": 1692204252
    },
    {
      "id": "64d39b8fe5172d00004cf425",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1691589520,
      "updated": 1691589520
    }
  ]
}